Definition: some situation or event that is thought about
Example: he kept drifting off the topic; he had been thinking about the subject for several years; it is a matter for the police
Synonyms: adj, pert, topical, subject, issue, matter, verb, stative, cognitive_content, some, situation, or, event, that, is, thought, about, he, kept, drifting, off, the, had, been, thinking, for, several, years, it, a, police
Category: noun.cognition
